3. cs.MM (Multimedia): The paper deals with processing and analyzing images of pedestrians, which can be considered as a multimedia application. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of deep learning techniques for person re-identification can be considered as an application of artificial intelligence.
